{
  "info": {
    "name": "VoltExchange API",
    "description": "Coleção completa de endpoints para testar a API VoltExchange — BD II 2025/2026\n\nBase URL: http://localhost:3000\nAutenticação: Bearer JWT (guardado automaticamente após login/register)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "🏥 Health",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Health Check",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/health",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "health"]
            },
            "description": "Verifica se a API está online. Não requer autenticação."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "🔐 Auth",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.token) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('token', res.token);",
                  "  console.log('Token guardado automaticamente');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"nome\": \"João Silva\",\n  \"email\": \"joao@voltexchange.com\",\n  \"password\": \"senha123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "register"]
            },
            "description": "Regista novo utilizador. Retorna JWT token guardado automaticamente na variável {{token}}.\n\nResposta 201:\n```json\n{ \"token\": \"...\", \"tipo\": \"Bearer\", \"email\": \"...\", \"nome\": \"...\" }\n```"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "const res = pm.response.json();",
                  "if (res.token) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('token', res.token);",
                  "  console.log('Token guardado automaticamente');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"joao@voltexchange.com\",\n  \"password\": \"senha123\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Autentica utilizador. Retorna JWT token guardado automaticamente na variável {{token}}.\n\nResposta 200:\n```json\n{ \"token\": \"...\", \"tipo\": \"Bearer\", \"email\": \"...\", \"nome\": \"...\" }\n```"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Login — Credenciais Inválidas",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"email\": \"joao@voltexchange.com\",\n  \"password\": \"passworderrada\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "login"]
            },
            "description": "Teste de segurança: credenciais inválidas devem retornar 401."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "⚡ Meters (Contadores)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Listar Contadores do Utilizador",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}", "type": "text" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/meters",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "meters"]
            },
            "description": "Lista contadores do utilizador autenticado.\n\nResposta 200:\n```json\n[\n  { \"contador_id\": 1, \"utilizador_id\": 1, \"numero_serie\": \"...\", \"estado\": \"ATIVO\", \"regiao\": \"Norte\" }\n]\n```"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Registar Leitura — Normal",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}", "type": "text" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"kwhLeitura\": 45.230,\n  \"dadosAudit\": {\n    \"temperatura\": 42,\n    \"voltagem\": 230,\n    \"erro_codigo\": null\n  }\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/meters/1/readings",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "meters", "1", "readings"]
            },
            "description": "Grava leitura normal (temperatura < 80, sem erro_codigo). ContadorId vai no path.\n\nResposta 201:\n```json\n{ \"mensagem\": \"Leitura registada com sucesso\", \"leituraId\": 1, \"dataHora\": \"...\", \"contadorId\": 1 }\n```"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Registar Leitura — Anomalia Temperatura (trigger ativa)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}", "type": "text" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"kwhLeitura\": 12.500,\n  \"dadosAudit\": {\n    \"temperatura\": 95,\n    \"voltagem\": 228,\n    \"erro_codigo\": null\n  }\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/meters/1/readings",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "meters", "1", "readings"]
            },
            "description": "Temperatura > 80 — o trigger trg_DetectarAnomalias muda contador para MANUTENCAO."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Registar Leitura — Anomalia erro_codigo (trigger ativa)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}", "type": "text" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"kwhLeitura\": 8.100,\n  \"dadosAudit\": {\n    \"temperatura\": 45,\n    \"voltagem\": 215,\n    \"erro_codigo\": \"ERR_042\"\n  }\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/meters/1/readings",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "meters", "1", "readings"]
            },
            "description": "Presença de erro_codigo — o trigger trg_DetectarAnomalias muda contador para MANUTENCAO."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Listar Leituras por Período",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}", "type": "text" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/meters/1/readings?inicio=2025-01-01T00:00:00&fim=2025-12-31T23:59:59",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "meters", "1", "readings"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "inicio", "value": "2025-01-01T00:00:00" },
                { "key": "fim", "value": "2025-12-31T23:59:59" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Lista leituras do contador 1 em 2025. Aproveita o particionamento por data_hora."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Acesso Sem Token (401)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/meters",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "meters"]
            },
            "description": "Teste de segurança: sem token deve retornar 401."
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "🔋 Market (Mercado)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Listar Ofertas Ativas",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}", "type": "text" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/market/offers",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "market", "offers"]
            },
            "description": "Lista ofertas com estado ATIVA, ordenadas por preço crescente."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Listar Ofertas por Região",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}", "type": "text" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/market/offers?regiao=Norte",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "market", "offers"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "regiao", "value": "Norte" }
              ]
            },
            "description": "Filtra ofertas ativas pela região Norte."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Criar Oferta de Venda",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}", "type": "text" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"quantidadeKwh\": 50.0,\n  \"precoUnitario\": 0.12,\n  \"regiao\": \"Norte\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/market/offers",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "market", "offers"]
            },
            "description": "Cria nova oferta de venda de energia.\n\nResposta 201: registo completo da oferta criada com estado='ATIVA'."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Compra Direta (sp_ExecutarCompraDireta)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}", "type": "text" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"quantidade\": 10.5\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/market/offers/1/buy",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "market", "offers", "1", "buy"]
            },
            "description": "Compra imediata via sp_ExecutarCompraDireta. OfertaId vai no path.\n\nACID: bloqueia oferta (SELECT FOR UPDATE), debita/credita saldos, insere Transacao.\n\nResposta 200:\n```json\n{ \"mensagem\": \"Compra realizada com sucesso\", \"ofertaId\": 1, \"quantidade\": 10.5 }\n```"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Criar Ordem de Compra Futura",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}", "type": "text" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"quantidadeKwh\": 20.0,\n  \"precoMaximo\": 0.15,\n  \"regiao\": \"Norte\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/market/order",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "market", "order"]
            },
            "description": "Cria ordem de compra futura com estado='PENDENTE'.\n\nResposta 201: registo completo da ordem criada."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Criar Ordem — Sem Região",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" },
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}", "type": "text" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"quantidadeKwh\": 5.0,\n  \"precoMaximo\": 0.20\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/market/order",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "market", "order"]
            },
            "description": "Ordem sem preferência de região — o matching aceita qualquer região."
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Disparar Matching Engine (sp_MatchingEngine)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}", "type": "text" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/market/match",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "market", "match"]
            },
            "description": "Dispara sp_MatchingEngine manualmente. OBRIGATÓRIO para avaliação.\n\nResposta 200:\n```json\n{ \"mensagem\": \"Matching engine executado com sucesso\" }\n```"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "🛠️ Admin",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Listar Anomalias JSONB",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}", "type": "text" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/anomalies",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "admin", "anomalies"]
            },
            "description": "Query JSONB com índice GIN: temperatura > 80 OU presença de erro_codigo.\n\nResposta 200:\n```json\n{\n  \"totalAnomalias\": 5,\n  \"contadoresEmManutencao\": 2,\n  \"leituras\": [...],\n  \"contadores\": [...]\n}\n```"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Listar Transações",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{token}}", "type": "text" }
            ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/admin/transactions",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "admin", "transactions"]
            },
            "description": "Histórico completo de transações (DIRETA e MATCHED).\n\nResposta 200:\n```json\n{\n  \"total\": 10,\n  \"transacoes\": [...]\n}\n```"
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
